    ==
  ::
  ++  on-save  !>(state)
  ++  on-load
    |=  old=vase
    ^-  (quip card _this)
    =|  cards=(list card)
    ::  new additions to app-state
    ::
    =|  spo=(map ship [residents=(set ship) requests=(set ship)])
    |^
    =+  !<(old-state=app-states old)
    =?  cards  ?=(%0 -.old-state)
